m/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2580951%2F%E9%97%9C%E6%84%9B%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E7%A0%94%E5%90%91%E6%96%B0%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E8%80%85%E6%B4%BE1%E8%90%AC%25E3%2580%2580%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%EF%BC%9A%E9%9C%80%E5%95%86%E8%A8%8E%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=ea1ab68c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2580951/關愛基金研向新來港者派1萬%E3%80%80基金成員：需商討如何發放</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.communitycarefund.hk/tc/ccf_committee/committee_members.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitycarefund.hk%2Ftc%2Fccf_committee%2Fcommittee_members.html&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=73fae08f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.communitycarefund.hk/tc/ccf_committee/committee_members.html</a><br />\n鄺俊宇都<strong>唔係</strong>關愛基金成員...<br />\nlist無佢個名 同埋港共點會委任民主派入去..."},{"pid":"9d27cdbb049691b6470752646c1a44b457c51342","tid":2215644,"uid":236414,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e69833a476c2b35bd601d742fadb82d59c429b07","tid":2215644,"uid":236414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:29:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72566407bd812889cf4b7a3921a2093df8dc9d42","tid":2215644,"uid":37111,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d27cdbb049691b6470752646c1a44b457c51342","tid":2215644,"uid":236414,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"29b058877a11dece3df47ae3b83e9d34dad99ca5","tid":2215644,"uid":37111,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c4d7d33c688a41fd5be3de4d30257d819d5199dd","tid":2215644,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地最愛既鄺神<br />\n夠唔夠薑咁答丫拿<br />\n「福利只係可以比合資格既本地居民<br />\n新移民未獲得正式既香港居留權<br />\n故此唔應該拎到一萬蚊<br />\n